~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : listen                                    ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : listen

   This is a toggle that lets you listen or not to the conversation 
   in the room and any shouts. This is usefull if you want to read 
   your mail or the message boards and you dont want any speech 
   appearing between pages.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
